OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBusiness group boss steps  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Faside after misconduct     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fclaims                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The boss of one of the UK's largest    
OL,6, business groups has stepped aside while
OL,7, an investigation takes place into      
OL,8, complaints about his conduct at work.  
OL,10,FThe CBI said it took all matters of    
OL,11,Fworkplace conduct "extremely           
OL,12,Fseriously", but would not comment      
OL,13,Ffurther until the probe was complete.  
OL,15,FIn a tweet, Tony Danker said he was    
OL,16,F"mortified" to hear that he had caused 
OL,17,F"offence or anxiety to any colleague". 
OL,19,F"It was completely unintentional, and I
OL,20,Fapologise profusely," he wrote.        
